description: This file contains function prototype declarations related to the internal API of the Slap Object Proxy component in the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP). It declares functions for setting object descriptors and creating new server proxy objects, specific to the internal implementation of the component.

methods.name: SlapOpoSetObjDescriptor
methods.description: Sets the object descriptor for the object proxy instance.

methods.name: SlapOpoNewSrvProxy
methods.description: Creates a new server proxy object associated with the SLAP object.
